00:08:58.820 --> 00:09:03.820
Even if you are facing the person without the fellow witness standing beside you,

00:09:03.820 --> 00:09:07.820
are you really all alone?

00:09:07.820 --> 00:09:15.820
Jesus knew that at the most stressful and emotionally draining time during his human life,

00:09:15.820 --> 00:09:22.820
his disciples would leave him all alone, but was he really alone?

00:09:22.820 --> 00:09:28.820
Let's read the inspired account at John 1632.

00:09:28.820 --> 00:09:31.820
