00:09:31.820 --> 00:09:38.820
Look, the hour is coming, indeed it has come, when each one of you will be scattered to his own house,

00:09:38.820 --> 00:09:46.820
and you will leave me alone, but I am not alone because the father is with me.

00:09:46.820 --> 00:09:54.820
Jesus was not alone during his most anxious moments, Jehovah was with him.

00:09:54.820 --> 00:10:01.820
